headline: Jabil Set to Report Q1 Earnings: Will Revenue Decline Impact Earnings?
summary: JBL is expected to report a revenue contraction year over year owing to soft demand in several verticals.

headline: Immersion (IMMR) Tops Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Immersion (IMMR) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 453.33% and 5,983.41%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
